---
description: Scope rule for Cursor mobile-development specialization files.
globs: "**/*"
alwaysApply: true
---

- Work only inside `cursor/mobile-development/` and mobile projects intentionally placed below it.
- Use native Cursor components only: `AGENTS.md`, `.cursor/agents`, `.cursor/skills`, `.cursor/rules`, `.cursor/hooks.json`, and `.cursor/hooks`.
- Do not create generic `agents`, `subagents`, `skills`, `workflows`, `hooks`, `mcp`, or `common` directories.
- Do not add active MCP servers by default.
- Do not modify another platform or specialization.
- Preserve the twelve specialist responsibilities and ten workflow Skills defined by `AGENTS.md`.
